title: Political Rally
new-page: true
is-card: true
tags: party_affairs
view-if: rally_timer <= 0
on-arrival: month_actions += 1; rally_timer = 6
card-image: img/ikada.png

Mass rallies are a common feature of our campaign media. What should the focus of this rally be?

- @pancasila: Upholding national unity under the <span style="color: #ffe924;">Pancasila</span> as the foundation of our nation.
- @marhaen: Promoting <span style="color: #990000;">Marhaenism</span> as an ideology of struggle for the people.
- @democracy: Expanding our nascent democracy and pushing for the creation of a new constitution.
- @pacifism: Pushing for our complete sovereignty and opposing western imperialism and colonialism at all costs!
- @wtb: Support the WTB plan!
- @local: A mixture of various local and national concerns that resonate most with the audience.
- @easy_discard

@pancasila
on-arrival: rural_pni += 2*(1-dissent); middle_pni += 2*(1-dissent); workers_pni += 2*(1-dissent);

#have this reduce rebellion support and strength

The message has lit up the fire of nationalism and unity within the heart of the people.

@marhaen
on-arrival: rural_pni += 4*(1-(partindo_dissent/100)); sidik_strength += 3; partindo_strength += 4; partindo_dissent -= 3;
face-image: img/soekarno_pni.jpg

<span style="color: #990000;">Marhaenism</span> is a socialistic ideology developed by President Sukarno and the guiding ideology of the <span style="color: #990000;">**PNI**</span>, emphasizing national unity, collectivist economics, and uplifting the rights of the <span class="tooltip-text" title="In his Indonesia Menggugat (Indonesia Accuses) speech in 1930, Sukarno used the term 'Marhaen' referring to the Indonesian agrarian class, replacing the 'Proletariat' as he considered it as irrelevant in Indonesia.">*Marhaens*</span>. 

Our message has greatly reinvigorated the patriotic spirit within the people, especially the agrarian *Marhaens*.

@democracy
on-arrival: democratization += 1; pro_republic += 2*(1 - dissent); rural_pni += 3*(1-dissent) if democratization >= 3; middle_pni += 3*(1-dissent) if democratization >= 3; pro_republic += 4*(1 - dissent) if democratization >= 3; middle_pni += 4*(1-dissent) if democratization >= 3 

Our speakers defend the <span style="color: #990000;">Socio</span>-Democratic system, promoting the participation of the people both in politics and in the economy, to achieve social justice and prosperity.

[? if democratization < 3 : Talk of democracy does not excite the rural as much as more practical issues, some even criticize it as "western propaganda". But that may change; part of our job is to provide political education to the people. ?]
[? if democratization >= 3 : Since we have consistently made democratization a theme of our campaign, the people are enthusiastic about our message. ?]

@pacifism
on-arrival: nationalism += 3*(1 - dissent); rural_pni += 2*(1 - dissent); unemployed_pni += 3*(1-dissent); middle_pni += 4*(1-dissent)

Our speakers denounce the military establishment and all the spending entering that black hole. Some adventurous speakers question the responsibility of the military elites in organizing the Great War.

@wtb
view-if: wtb_adopted = 1
choose-if: return_to_normalcy = 0
unavailable-subtitle: The economic crisis is largely over now, and the public is no longer interested in hearing about it.
on-arrival: wtb_support += 1; rural_pni += 6*(1-dissent); unemployed_pni += 6*(1-dissent); rural_pni += 3*(1-dissent); new_middle_pni += 3*(1-dissent); old_middle_pni += 3*(1-dissent);

The WTB plan has become a popular rallying cry for our party. The rural are eager to go back to work, and that is exactly what the plan promises.


@local
on-arrival: rural_pni += 3*(1-dissent); middle_pni += 2*(1-dissent); aristocrats_pni += 3*(1-dissent);

Our speakers have gauged the mood and are speaking to the issues that seem to most affect the people in this moment.
